				"url": "https://saviynt-product.aha.io/requirements/FON-910-1",
				"resource": "https://saviynt-product.aha.io/api/v1/requirements/FON-910-1",
				"description": {
					"id": "7509459848936466505",
					"body": "Hi Team,\u003cbr\u003e \u003cbr\u003e  We have identified a validation discrepancy between the UI and the API when uploading data files with filename having space. For example, when attempting to upload a file with the name EA-Portal_Sandbox via the UI, we receive a validation error/message\u003cbr\u003e \u003cbr\u003e However, when using the API (/ECM/api/v5/uploadSchemaFile) for import, this validation is bypassed, allowing the file to be uploaded regardless of its name.\u003cbr\u003e \u003cbr\u003e Thank you\u003cbr\u003e \u003cbr\u003e Pooja Kumari",
					"editor_version": 1,
					"created_at": "2025-05-28T11:39:30.120Z",
					"updated_at": "2025-05-28T11:39:30.120Z",
					"attachments": []
				},
