						"name": "Acceptance Criteria",
						"updatedAt": "2025-05-28T11:39:30Z",
						"value": "API should honour file name as in UI\r\n\r\nAPI should throw Error “Invalid file Name” when file name has white space or special characters. {This is same as in UI}",
