						"name": "Acceptance Criteria",
						"updatedAt": "2025-06-23T14:42:03Z",
						"value": "When files in the success folder are deleted from UI.\r\n\r\nIt should allow you to delete the file.\r\n\r\n( Background- If the files are placed in the success folder outside of Saviynt process say may be a JAR- then it throws null exception and prevents deletion but works fine for files pushed from within Saviynt)",
